<h1> Best Movies according to me</h1>
<h2>My top 3 movies of 2023. </h2>
<hr/>
<h3>1.Oppenheimer</h3>
<p>The story of American scientist J. Robert Oppenheimer and his role in the development of the atomic bomb.</p>
<p>Director: Christopher Nolan | Stars: Cillian Murphy, Emily Blunt, Matt Damon, Robert Downey Jr.</p>

<h3>2. Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One</h3>
<p>Ethan Hunt and his IMF team must track down a dangerous weapon before it falls into the wrong hands.</p>
<p>Director: Christopher McQuarrie | Stars: Tom Cruise, Hayley Atwell, Ving Rhames, Simon Pegg</p>

<h3>3.Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3</h3>
<p>Still reeling from the loss of Gamora, Peter Quill rallies his team to defend the universe and one of their own - a mission that could mean the end of the Guardians if not successful.</p>
<p>Director: James Gunn | Stars: Chris Pratt, Chukwudi Iwuji, Bradley Cooper, Pom Klementieff</p>
